splash.track-bp-bs-meds: Mundeete xiiwo (BP), mundeekki sukkaare, nna xaggakki harunsi.
consent.using-this-app: Tenne app/e horonsiratenni umikki mashallaqqe calla e’anni nooro buuxi woyi wolootu su’minni eessate fajjantewota ikkase buuxi.
consent.any-data-stored: Tenne app(appera) eessitinoyiti  ayi mashalaqe bilbiliki uduunnichi  giddo duunantewota ikkitehura  tenne appe(app) kalaqaanchira  woyi wole ayi bissarano dissa’anno. Appete(app) horonsira daafira afantewokki titirshuwate mashalaquwa harunsatenni  hakka appete(app) kalaqaanchiwa sa’ara dandiitanno.
consent.more-information: Taje hiittoonni agarsiinsemoronna mittunnita ikkase(privacy) buuxate ledote taje {here} afantara dandiitanno.
consent.medical-disclaimer: Tenne appe horonsirate gari hatto hikkiminnu amaale gede ikkite la”ama dinose nna dottoraho woyi woluutu keeranchimate gargaraano ogeeyye bayichono dikkitanno (ikkitarano didaanditanno) Hatto “jawa” “Co'icha” “shiima” noori wo’mante Mundeete xiiwo nna Mundeete sukkaare badooshu baalu Mundeete xiiwo nna Mundeete sukkaare su’misate gudde adhamooshshu noonsa qaafuwa ledo sumuu yitannona hallanshichaho baxxitewo amaale diuyitanno. Tenne appe horonsira’nera albaanni  dottora’ne amaa’le.
